DeadRSX is a high level library for rsx devlopment and are library only supported in PSL1GHT SDK
ooPo libraries may also be required for use of DeadRSX

supported features --------------------------------------------------
screen scale - (scale the screen depending on size SAFE AREA 847x511)

functions -
drsx_init(); // basic screen stuff and scaling code connects to this
drsx_alpha();  // enables alpha blending
drsx_background(); // change background color
drsx_loadPNG(); // load a png from outside of memory from a device or location
drsx_loadBIN(); // load bin from memory
drsx_CPNG_IMG(); // converts PngDatas to Image
drsx_drawSprite(); // draw sprite to the cord you pick



